<h1>Search a Pick up point</h1>
<span>
  You can search by the zipcode, the country code, or find all the points we have around the world.<br />
  Our locations are distributed in three countries, but we are groing fast, dont worry if you country is not here.
</span>
<section class="container pb-3 ">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <form action="/search" method="GET">
        <div class="input-group mb-3">
          <div class="input-group-prepend">
            <span class="input-group-text">Zip Code</span>
          </div>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" name="zipCode">
          <button type="submit">Submit</button>
        </div>
      </form>
      <form action="/search" method="GET">
        <div class="input-group mb-3">
          <div class="input-group-prepend">
            <span class="input-group-text">Country Code</span>
          </div>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" name="countryCode">
          <button type="submit">Submit</button>
        </div>
      </form>
      {{#each places}}
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">{{this.name}}</h5>
          <p class="card-text">{{this.address}}</p>
          <div class="row">
            <span class="col">{{this.countryCode}}</span>
            <span class="col">{{this.zipCode}}</span>
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseExample"
            aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
            Check the location
          </button>
          <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
            <div class="card card-body">
              Anim pariatur cliche reprehenderit, enim eiusmod high life accusamus terry richardson ad squid. Nihil anim
              keffiyeh helvetica, craft beer labore wes anderson cred nesciunt sapiente ea proident.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
